&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_block&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;At BPD, we’re always looking to build relationships with passionate, talented individuals who want to ignite greatness by delivering the future to healthcare&#39;s leading brands. Don&#39;t see a current opening thats quite that perfect fit? No worries, we still want to hear from you!&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;Share your resume and a brief note about why you’re interested in working at BPD.&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;If there’s a potential match, our People Team will reach out to start a conversation — especially with candidates located near our offices in&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Boca Raton, FL&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;or&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Nashville, TN&lt;/strong&gt;, where we believe in the power of in-person collaboration to spark big ideas and meaningful connections.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Join our talent community and stay connected with BPD for future opportunities.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
